  "title": "Senior Technical",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Highlights</strong></u></p><p>Positive Working Environment</p><p>Career Advancement</p><p>Engaging Culture</p><p><br /></p><p><u>Job Description</u></p><h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Perform installation of instruments and maintenance works</li><li>Control maintenance process and issues</li><li>Contribute to continuous improvements</li><li>Interpret drawings or data to troubleshoot or execute work/ defects</li><li>Carry out routine preventive maintenance works</li><li>Record equipment performance in assigned lines</li><li>Suggest improvements in equipment set-up</li><li>Keep records of a diagnosis or defective final products</li><li>Take initiative to seek opportunities for improvements and implement corrective action</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Professional Certifications, NITEC and/ or Diploma holder</li><li>Singapore class 3 driving license</li><li>This job requires physical work and working outdoor such as site visitation and inspection</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Additional Information</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Career Level</strong></p><p>Non-Executive</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Qualification</strong></p><p>Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Type</strong></p><p>Full-Time</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Specialization</strong></p><p>Installation, schedule <a href=\"https://www.jobstreet.com.sg/en/job-search/maintenance-repair-facilities-machinery-jobs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Maintenance</a> etc</p><p><br /></p><p>Company Overview</p><p>Incorporated in 1994, Oxen is an IT technology company specializing in the distribution and maintenance of monitoring systems for construction sites. Our monitoring applications include noise monitoring system, earth control measurement (ECM), vibration monitoring system, turnstiles, Skycam and CCTV monitoring systems for construction sites.</p>",
